node.text: In the blink of an eye, you’re now 1. No longer a baby, but a toddler. You made your first steps, beginning to reveal your character and eye for trouble. Thank you for bringing such joy into our lives. Mummy and daddy loves you tremendously. @ferlyyy_  and I are also deeply touched by all the kindness and love we’ve received from family and friends. From surprise meals to gift drops, well wishes, kind messages and heartfelt calls. Thank you, from the bottom of our hearts. #babygirl #family #love #CBparty #circuitbreakersg #circuitbreaker
